              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>As many relevant ones as possible. Google recommends at least 4 sitelinks, 4 callouts, and 2 structured snippets. The more options Google has, the more likely it is to display extensions with your ad.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
